THANK YOU FOR THE OPPORTUNITY TO HELP YOU FIND A NEW HOME! TO LEARN MORE ABOUT MY SERVICE PLEASE READ THE INFORMATION BELOW.

I sale and lease properties all over Austin and Central Texas including apartments, duplexes, condos, townhomes, and of course houses. Do you have a friend who is looking for a new place to call home? Let me know and I'll give you a referral fee!


My service is FREE to you but.....

.....if you are interested in leasing a condo, townhome, duplex, or house please know in order for me to get credit for helping you to find your new home I have to show you the property. If I send you a list of available rental properties let me know which properties you're interested in viewing and I will make the all the necessary arrangements for you including; appointments to view property with tenants, other realtors, and management companies and processing your application.

.....if you are interested in leasing an apartment most apartments require that I make an appointment to show you the apartments but some allow me to give you the information and register you so you can stop by at your convenience. If I send you a list of available apartments it's important that you check with me on which you can see without me and which I have to show you in order to get credit in the event you decide to lease. It's also important to remember to put my name on the apartment guest card and application so that the property management company knows I referred you.

.....if you are interested in buying a property please remember to let builders and other Realtors know you are working with me.

Thank you for helping me to make a living helping nice people like you to find a new place to call home!

Bill Bill Roquemore Broker, CRS, GRI, ABR Prestige Realty Your Real Estate Professional 512-627-4286 www.Prestige-Austin.com Why choose a CRS? The Council of Residential Specialist (CRS) is the highest Designation awarded to Realtors® in residential Real Estate by the Council of Residential Specialists. The CRS Designation recognizes professional accomplishments in both experience and education. Since 1977 the Council of Residential Specialists has been conferring the CRS Designation on agents who meet its stringent requirements. Today less than 4% of all Realtors® have earned the designation. Choose only the best -a CRS- to help you, your family and friends with today's demanding Real Estate needs.
